monitoring and logging  module

comunication device:
Serial:   logging
Serial1:  polling and receive logging messages
I2C: RTC , display
pins: buzzer
pins: encoder

task:
watchdog management with alarm on reboot
read datetime from RTC at boot
wait for polling message and alarm when timeout happen
read logging messages, add timestamp and append it to SDcard

function managed by encoder:
* alarm reset
* alarm test
* activate/deactivate alarm function
* datetime setting and save it on RTC
